### Quick Start Examples for Todo App API
### Use these requests to quickly test the main functionality

### ================================
### GETTING STARTED
### ================================

### 1. Welcome - Test the connection
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/simple-chat/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Hello, how can you help me with my todos?"
}

### ================================
### BASIC TODO CREATION
### ================================

### 2. Create your first todo
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/simple-chat/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "I need to buy milk and bread"
}

### 3. Create a work task
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/simple-chat/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Prepare presentation for Monday meeting"
}

### ================================
### VIEW YOUR TODOS
### ================================

### 4. See all your todos
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/simple-chat/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What todos do I have?"
}

### ================================
### ADVANCED EXAMPLES
### ================================

### 5. Create multiple todos at once
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/simple-chat/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "I need to schedule a doctor appointment, buy groceries, and finish the quarterly report"
}

### 6. Get todos by category
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/simple-chat/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What shopping items do I need to buy?"
}

### 7. Clear all todos (be careful!)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/simple-chat/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Delete all my todos"
}
